# Adam Enfroy — Affiliate Marketing

Complete affiliate marketing system for building profitable hobby niche blogs using AI content velocity, infinite keyword loops, and layered monetization (Mediavine ads + affiliate commissions).

## Overview

Adam Enfroy's methodology: Find a hobby niche you genuinely enjoy, discover infinite keyword loops that produce unlimited top-of-funnel traffic, build a three-tier content funnel that moves readers from discovery to purchase, and monetize with Mediavine display ads (floor income) plus three focused affiliate programs (ceiling income). AI handles 70% of content production; you add the expertise and trust signals that convert.

**Core Insight**: Pick a hobby niche with beatable competition, find one keyword with 20+ variations, publish 30-40 posts in 90 days, qualify for Mediavine, then layer affiliate revenue on top.

