## Recommended Workflow

```
1. Validate niche          → 01-niche-validation
2. Discover keyword loops  → infinite-keyword-loop
3. Select affiliate stack  → affiliate-program-selector
4. Design content funnel   → content-funnel-architect
5. Plan ad revenue sprint  → ad-revenue-accelerator
6. Build 6-month roadmap   → 02-90-day-plan
7. Write discovery posts   → 03-ai-article (Tier 1)
8. Build topical authority  → 05-topical-authority
9. Map buyer funnel        → 11-buyer-psychology
10. Write comparison posts → affiliate-comparison-post
11. Launch second platform → traffic-diversification
```

## Core Principles

- **Hobby Niches**: Pick niches where competition is other hobbyists, not Forbes
- **Infinite Keyword Loops**: Find one keyword with 20+ variations for unlimited content
- **Three-Tier Funnel**: Discovery (ads) → Education (trust) → Conversion (affiliate)
- **Ad Revenue Floor**: Mediavine pays for all expenses; affiliate revenue is pure profit
- **AI Leverage**: AI produces 70% of content; human adds expertise and trust signals
- **Three-Program Focus**: Deep expertise on 3 affiliate programs beats scattered links on 20

